column5: Anyone know where I can pick up a cheap air compressor unit? I went to Canadian tire the other day and they told me thy only had 12v or super expensive ones - neither of which is what I want and need.  Wal-mart had a few in their camping section, but prices were not as good as I expected.  any ideas? It does not need to be high power, and I would prefer if it was small (its for attaching to a powder coat system I will be using for my lures)

hey mepps,i dont know if you have a princess auto near london where you are but its a discount auto parts chain and man they are just like a home depot,they have everything and i know they have small compressors...check them out online or go to one near you im in oshawa and they have one in whitby..so hope this helped.good luck     cheers
Yes, there is a Princess Auto location in London.  Here ya go Clive.  My Webpage
Thanks guys, I'll check em out tomorrow!
ebay  Theres almost nothing you cant get there ...
